<div class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Защо да изберете TopDriveX?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-red-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                    <span class="text-5xl">🔍</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Лесно търсене</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Намерете автомобила, който търсите бързо и лесно с нашите мощни филтри</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-red-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                    <span class="text-5xl">✅</span>
