            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-red-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                    <span class="text-5xl">💬</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Директна връзка</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Свържете се директно с продавача без посредници</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
